      528.74,
      538.56,
      643.51
    ],
    "text": "Issued at 04.00 p.m. on 18 April 2026. Atmospheric conditions for evening thundershowers are expected to be favorable in most parts of the island from the 20th of April onwards. Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Central, Sabaragamuwa, Uva, North-western and Southern provinces after 1.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.920000076293945,
      12.0,
